{"word":"H5031 - נְבִיאָה - nᵉbîyʼâh - neb-ee-yaw' - Prophetess","slug":"H5031","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נְבִיאָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>nᵉbîyʼâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>neb-ee-yaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Prophetess"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E0;&#x05D1;&#x05D9;&#x05D0;&#x05D4; - n<sup>e</sup>b&#x0131;&#x0302;y'a&#x0302;h</b> - <i>neb-ee-yaw'</i><p/>Feminine of <a href=\"#/H5030\">H5030</a>; a <i>prophetess</i> or (generally) <i>inspired</i> woman; by implication a <i>poetess</i>; by association a <i>prophet's wife: - </i>prophetess."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5012\">H5012</a>, <a href=\"#/H5016\">H5016</a>, <a href=\"#/H5030\">H5030</a>"}]}